{"tid":2455633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[over my dead body] 包致金稱無意離開終審法院：盡力做好本份　法官不應介入政治爭議","createTime":"2021-03-21T09:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T09:41:12.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae68b9324cae0047511a248f60a02118d36fd60","tid":2455633,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2451483/org/867426a8e360674c614f4ab473b918d9.jpg/gGzUZm4wZ2ZYqd7aH_xYc5Il9pLOjPY5egc5tnoHObY?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2451483%2Forg%2F867426a8e360674c614f4ab473b918d9.jpg%2FgGzUZm4wZ2ZYqd7aH_xYc5Il9pLOjPY5egc5tnoHObY%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=abff0c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國最高法院院長、香港終審法院海外法官韋彥德（Lord Robert Reed）日前表示，若香港出現破壞司法獨立、法庭違反法治的情況，基於良知不能做下去的話，會辭任終院法官。終審法院非常任法官包致金今日（21日）表示，有關英籍非常任法官應否離任討論是「不幸」，強調法官不應介入政治爭議，他無打算離開司法機構。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210321/450335568014872576143760.jpeg/nmEd4JWhHYe9H9Mgeg0UyNbI20zG3fpxSxNUsUsTVLE?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210321%2F450335568014872576143760.jpeg%2FnmEd4JWhHYe9H9Mgeg0UyNbI20zG3fpxSxNUsUsTVLE%3Fv%3Dw640&h=54ed4b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3707050/org/d6b379bbd0bb1996a6396af218e4f983.jpg/FYvFKy3o_6xpk8IP7fmteIhAs1C2MeQkQY8iDEGPIgw?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3707050%2Forg%2Fd6b379bbd0bb1996a6396af218e4f983.jpg%2FFYvFKy3o_6xpk8IP7fmteIhAs1C2MeQkQY8iDEGPIgw%3Fv%3Dw640&h=78717692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年73歲的包致金，今早到鴨脷洲體育館接種復必泰疫苗，他形容自己是「疫苗信徒」，不止對自己有益，亦對家庭及社會有益，又指即使接種疫苗後有副作用，仍會繼續，因副作用不會影響他人，包括孫兒，但新型冠狀病毒會。至於為何選擇復必泰，他說有較多數據，但只有科興疫苗，他亦會接種。<br />\n<br />\n對於韋彥德近日出席英國聽證會，稱若不能再以良心服務，將辭任終院法官，包致金形容是近日爭議「不幸」，但他對此不感恐懼，對司法機構甚具信心，亦希望港人繼續相信香港法院，他會繼續做好本份。"},{"pid":"b0c0e9370646b76bf8d953cbb6a6f5efded5bb74","tid":2455633,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"人上人地位梗係好，最公正添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52bf139932997289908d468bdcc1a0374b80cbc6","tid":2455633,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"Amina 幾時再摑柒d狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbc717877e929166f57cb735a764bd092f5685e","tid":2455633,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52bf139932997289908d468bdcc1a0374b80cbc6","tid":2455633,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"Amina 幾時再摑柒d狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100127172034/uncyclopedia/images/7/75/I_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages2.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20100127172034%2Funcyclopedia%2Fimages%2F7%2F75%2FI_w&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=bf778a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100127172034/uncyclopedia/images/7/75/I_w</a><img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LJ3YTS7LH6WP4T5KQX5A64U2XY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLJ3YTS7LH6WP4T5KQX5A64U2XY.gif&h=7758c470&s={SIZE}\" />anna_leave!.gif[/img]"},{"pid":"24eeb4bbc08ec276555591b991a71a5141eb3648","tid":2455633,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dbc717877e929166f57cb735a764bd092f5685e","tid":2455633,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52bf139932997289908d468bdcc1a0374b80cbc6","tid":2455633,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"